Package com.krupizde.command

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckCommand
    Class represents Command for checking again non-valid profiles (they got unbanned etc..)
    Command
    Parent class for command pattern used in interactive mode.
    CommandControl
    An execution class for command pattern
    DeleteNonvalidsCommand
    Class representing command for exporting and deleting non-valid profiles from database
    ExitCommand
    Class represents command, that ends interactive mode of application
    ExportCommand
    Class represents command, that exports all valid profiles to given file 'Valds.txt'
    GetNonvalidsCommand
    Class representing command, that prints non-valid profiles to console and exports them to file 'Exports.txt'
    GetPrivatesCommand
    Class represents command, that exports all private profiles from database to file 'Privates.txt'
    HelpCommand
    Class represents command, that prints all avaible command and their descriptions to console
    ListCommand
    Class represents command, that prints all profiles from database to console
    LoadNamesCommand
    Class represents command, that loads all names from set file to database
    ResetDatabase
    Class represents command, that deletes all data from database
